</span><br>Clash with various creatures using a multitude of weapons: melee, ranged, and throwing including spears, bows and clubs. Use Serum to infuse and modify your weapons and gain the upper hand against mutated abominations that roam the island.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1610520/extras/faee2fccea27e6efa0c945325b420222.poster.avif?t=1746119588\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1610520/extras/faee2fccea27e6efa0c945325b420222.webm?t=1746119588\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1610520/extras/4b88408e79e2171b7f1b3f749470f039.webp?t=1746119588\" width=600 height=45 /></span><br>Endure in a hostile environment under the pressure of time. Manage your health, stamina, and beware of Serum side effects.",
